The paper presents an algorithm for online multiclass learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The algorithm is designed to minimize regret, which is a common objective in online learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
